      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 36,
      "message": "1. Please don't use a complex data structure. Create an interface and implementation that describe it. \n2. Don't create an instance of the default size if you only need an empty map.\n3. HashMap is not thread safe. You may get unexpected results if an instance of this class is shared among multiple threads.",
